 A wise son makes his father glad: but a foolish son is a grief to his mother. }{\f1\fs16\insrsid2439857\charrsid2439857 2.}{\cs32\f35\fs32\insrsid2439857\charrsid2439857 
 Treasures shall not profit the lawless: but righteousness shall deliver from death. }{\f1\fs16\insrsid2439857\charrsid2439857 3.}{\cs32\f35\fs32\insrsid2439857\charrsid2439857  The Lord will not famish a righteous soul: bu
t he will overthrow the life of the ungodly. }{\f1\fs16\insrsid2439857\charrsid2439857 4.}{\cs32\f35\fs32\insrsid2439857\charrsid2439857  Poverty brings a man low: but the hands of the vigorous make rich. A son wh}{\cs32\f35\fs32\insrsid2439857 
o is instructed shall be wise, and shall use the fool for a servant. }{\f1\fs16\insrsid2439857\charrsid2439857 5.}{\cs32\f35\fs32\insrsid2439857\charrsid2439857  A wise son is saved from heat: but a lawless son is blighted of the winds in harvest. }{
\f1\fs16\insrsid2439857\charrsid2439857 6.}{\cs32\f35\fs32\insrsid2439857\charrsid2439857  The blessing of the Lord is upon the head of the just: but untimely grief shall cover the mouth}{\cs32\f35\fs32\insrsid2439857  of the ungodly. }{
\f1\fs16\insrsid2439857\charrsid2439857 7.}{\cs32\f35\fs32\insrsid2439857\charrsid2439857  The memory of the just is praised; but the name of the ungodly man is extinguished. }{\f1\fs16\insrsid2439857\charrsid2439857 8.}{
\cs32\f35\fs32\insrsid2439857\charrsid2439857  A wise man in heart will receive commandments; but he that is unguarded in his lips shall be overthrown in his perverseness. }{\f1\fs16\insrsid2439857\charrsid2439857 9.}{
\cs32\f35\fs32\insrsid2439857\charrsid2439857  He that walks simply, walks confidently; but he that perverts his ways shall be known. }{\f1\fs16\insrsid2439857\charrsid2439857 10.}{\cs32\f35\fs32\insrsid2439857\charrsid2439857 
 He that winks with his eyes deceitfully, procures griefs for men; but he that reproves boldly is a peacemaker. }{\f1\fs16\insrsid2439857\charrsid2439857 11.}{\cs32\f35\fs32\insrsid2439857\charrsid2439857  There is a fountain of life in the hand of a righ
}{\cs32\f35\fs32\insrsid2439857 teous man; but destruction shall cover the mouth of the ungodly. }{\f1\fs16\insrsid2439857\charrsid2439857 12.}{\cs32\f35\fs32\insrsid2439857\charrsid2439857  Hatred stirs up strife; but affection covers all that do no
t love strife. }{\f1\fs16\insrsid2439857\charrsid2439857 13.}{\cs32\f35\fs32\insrsid2439857\charrsid2439857  He that brings forth wisdom from his lips smites the fool with a rod. }{\f1\fs16\insrsid2439857\charrsid2439857 14.}{
\cs32\f35\fs32\insrsid2439857\charrsid2439857  The wise will hide discretion; but }{\cs32\f35\fs32\insrsid2439857 the mouth of the hasty draws near to ruin. }{\f1\fs16\insrsid2439857\charrsid2439857 15.}{\cs32\f35\fs32\insrsid2439857\charrsid2439857 
 The wealth of rich men is a strong city; but poverty is the ruin of the ungodly. }{\f1\fs16\insrsid2439857\charrsid2439857 16.}{\cs32\f35\fs32\insrsid2439857\charrsid2439857 
 The works of the righteous produce life; but the fruits of the ungodly produce sins. }{\f1\fs16\insrsid2439857\charrsid2439857 17.}{\cs32\f35\fs32\insrsid2439857\charrsid2439857  Instruction keeps the right ways of}{\cs32\f35\fs32\insrsid2439857 
 life; but instruction unchastened goes astray. }{\f1\fs16\insrsid2439857\charrsid2439857 18.}{\cs32\f35\fs32\insrsid2439857\charrsid2439857  Righteous lips cover enmity; but they that utter railings are most foolish. }{
\f1\fs16\insrsid2439857\charrsid2439857 19.}{\cs32\f35\fs32\insrsid2439857\charrsid2439857  By a multitude of words thou shalt not escape sin; but if thou refrain thy lips thou wilt be prudent. }{\f1\fs16\insrsid2439857\charrsid2439857 20.}{
\cs32\f35\fs32\insrsid2439857\charrsid2439857  The tongue of the }{\cs32\f35\fs32\insrsid2439857 just is tried silver; but the heart of the ungodly shall fail. }{\f1\fs16\insrsid2439857\charrsid2439857 21.}{\cs32\f35\fs32\insrsid2439857\charrsid2439857 
 The lips of the righteous know sublime truths: but the foolish die in want. }{\f1\fs16\insrsid2439857\charrsid2439857 22.}{\cs32\f35\fs32\insrsid2439857\charrsid2439857 
 The blessing of the Lord is upon the head of the righteous; it enriches him, and grief of heart shall not be }{\cs32\f35\fs32\insrsid2439857 added to it. }{\f1\fs16\insrsid2439857\charrsid2439857 
