\cs32\f35\fs32\insrsid2439857\charrsid2439857  Therefore every hand shall become powerless, and every soul of man shall be dismayed. }{\f1\fs16\insrsid2439857\charrsid2439857 8.}{\cs32\f35\fs32\insrsid2439857\charrsid2439857 
 The elders shall be troubled, and pangs shall seize them, as of a woman in travail: and they shall mourn one to another, and shall be amazed, and shal}{\cs32\f35\fs32\insrsid2439857 l change their countenance as a flame. }{
\f1\fs16\insrsid2439857\charrsid2439857 9.}{\cs32\f35\fs32\insrsid2439857\charrsid2439857  For behold! the day of the Lord is coming which cannot be escaped, of wrath and anger, to make the world desolate, and to destroy sinners out of it. }{
\f1\fs16\insrsid2439857\charrsid2439857 10.}{\cs32\f35\fs32\insrsid2439857\charrsid2439857  For the stars of heaven, and Orion, and all the host of heave}{\cs32\f35\fs32\insrsid2439857 
n, shall not give their light; and it shall be dark at sunrise, and the moon shall not give her light. }{\f1\fs16\insrsid2439857\charrsid2439857 11.}{\cs32\f35\fs32\insrsid2439857\charrsid2439857 
 And I will command evils for the whole world, and [will visit] their sins on the ungodly: and I will destroy the pride of transgressors, and will bri}{\cs32\f35\fs32\insrsid2439857 ng low the pride of the haughty. }{
\f1\fs16\insrsid2439857\charrsid2439857 12.}{\cs32\f35\fs32\insrsid2439857\charrsid2439857  And they that are left shall be more precious than gold tried by fire; and a man shall be more precious than the stone that is in Suphir. }{
\f1\fs16\insrsid2439857\charrsid2439857 13.}{\cs32\f35\fs32\insrsid2439857\charrsid2439857  For the heaven shall be enraged, and the earth shall be shaken from her found}{\cs32\f35\fs32\insrsid2439857 
